    "name": "Sands of Aura",
    "steam_appid": 1119840,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/2475f6e30902f3909cda1bc0abc7f21c.poster.avif?t=1771277747\" width=630 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/2475f6e30902f3909cda1bc0abc7f21c.webm?t=1771277747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >很久以前，一名饱受折磨的神祇引发了灭顶之灾，从此，塔拉姆赫尔陷入永夜。时间沙漏被打碎，沙子洒向大地，化为一望无际的沙海。曾经欣欣向荣的塔拉姆赫尔不复往日荣光，成为一片腐朽之地；而此地人民只剩腐烂的躯壳，化成野蛮暴力、不灭不屈的亡灵士兵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但塔拉姆赫尔没有消失，至少现在还没有。一代又一代，尽管正义之士寥寥无几，他们却始终坚守着这个国家。而你正是其中一员。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >余晖骑士团是人类最后的保护者，就在你加入他们的前夕，塔拉姆赫尔再度面临灾难。暗夜瘟疫的腐化本质突变了，人类王国比以往任何时候都更需要余晖骑士。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追踪并摧毁出现的邪恶。保卫人类王国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/4ffb13958a19188eac5c68bdb3ec94e3.webp?t=1771277747\" width=630 height=9 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/997bfd5d9b57a6d8e4cfc4e1ae2630a9.avif?t=1771277747\" width=630 height=67 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/a6f1a0d089627334a415e5fba339d9fb.poster.avif?t=1771277747\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/a6f1a0d089627334a415e5fba339d9fb.webm?t=1771277747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/a6f1a0d089627334a415e5fba339d9fb.mp4?t=1771277747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驶灵活的沙船“唤谷”，穿越危险的沙海，直面新型恐怖的源头，但别指望会有灯塔或地图上的标记为你指路。规划自己的前行道路：在这片茫茫沙海上，选择最合适的航向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过，驾驶“唤谷”时的冒险各不相同，流沙总是变幻莫测，未知的秘密、潜伏的危险、隐藏的道路将在眼前展开。事物并非看上去那样……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 塔拉姆赫尔是一个开放世界，尽情探索吧！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 每座岛屿都会带来无与伦比的美妙奇遇。精彩战斗、神奇传说、丰富财宝等你光临。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 挑战不同难度等级的副本，获得相应奖励。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 沙海航行并非孤军奋战，一位值得信赖的亡灵同伴会在瞭望台上休息。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/4ffb13958a19188eac5c68bdb3ec94e3.webp?t=1771277747\" width=630 height=9 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/2a0bc3a7ce65f54c5b2e852fb0756463.avif?t=1771277747\" width=630 height=67 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/8ce0f4380b4f3f1388e74809a652db62.poster.avif?t=1771277747\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/8ce0f4380b4f3f1388e74809a652db62.webm?t=1771277747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/8ce0f4380b4f3f1388e74809a652db62.mp4?t=1771277747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在塔拉姆赫尔的腐化造就了一个由人类与其他塔拉姆赫尔种族共同组成的部落。这些种族包括可敬的费伦与形似昆虫、具有蜂巢意识的哈沙拉。昔日交战的国家变成了一支罪大恶极、怨恨滔天的军队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从末日信徒到堕落国王，敌人守着你所寻求的答案，一心要你死。准备好迎接冷酷无情的战斗，别掉以轻心。亲爱的骑士，挥动你手中的武器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不计其数的武器部件散落在残破的文明遗迹之中，成千上万种特殊武器等你铸造。找到称手的兵器吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 7种战斗风格，斩开腐化，破浪前行。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 数十套防护盔甲，各具独特的防护功能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 魔法增强功能，可调整搭配攻击效果，打造你的流派。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/4ffb13958a19188eac5c68bdb3ec94e3.webp?t=1771277747\" width=630 height=9 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/78f53ffe2fd3d5d82a9fa56ff519dae7.avif?t=1771277747\" width=630 height=67 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/be82cf1f1060698be8ccbb4824beef9b.poster.avif?t=1771277747\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/be82cf1f1060698be8ccbb4824beef9b.webm?t=1771277747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/be82cf1f1060698be8ccbb4824beef9b.mp4?t=1771277747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“星塔”是你的圣殿，你的家，它的大门一直向你所认可的人敞开。。旅途中，你将遇到寻求庇护的难民，而一名余晖骑士可以看到他们在“星塔”中找到了圣殿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然值得加入 “星塔”的居民在加入后会使此地更强大、更安全，但不是所有人都值得加入“星塔”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“星塔”可以从领导力与判断力的角度测试你的余晖特质（游戏可选核心玩法）你对“星塔”居民的选择将改变你的故事，影响你与他人的命运，但前提是你得做出选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 新居民入住“星塔”将解锁特长，例如打造特殊道具或提供特殊服务等。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 探索他人生活、选择与行为，并决定他们的命运。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 与前所未有的人物互动，重建新社区。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 面对难辨是非的灰色难题，艰难的抉择在等着你。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/4ffb13958a19188eac5c68bdb3ec94e3.webp?t=1771277747\" width=630 height=9 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/3e9e324ac8754ce966609e24624ff339.avif?t=1771277747\" width=630 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由爱德华多·洛佩斯（Eduardo Lopez）监制并创造的《沙之交响曲》带来了栩栩如生、回味无穷的听觉盛宴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Sands of Aura》以完整的交响乐配乐为特色，采用多种音乐表现形式，从古老的维奥尔琴悠扬的弦乐，到保加利亚合唱团嘹亮的歌声，应有尽有。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是塔拉姆赫尔令人难忘的歌声，吟唱着这个伤痕累累的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119840/extras/49e32588fbe86bff980c1d875e323a6d.webp?t=1771277747\" width=630 height=33 /></span></p>",
